GSD.product_version: versions from v3.13 to before v4.19.268
GSD.description:
net: hsr: Fix potential use-after-free

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.19.268 by commit b35d899854d5d5d58eb7d7e7c0f61afc60d3a9e9, it was introduced in version v3.13 by commit f421436a591d34fa5279b54a96ac07d70250cc8d. For more details please see the references link.
